\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 6. S. confusa} Iljin, {\i Acta Horti Petrop.}{\b  26:} 284 (1930). Annual up to 50 cm, often woody at the base. Leaves 10-25 × c. 1 mm, semi-cylindrical, acute, acuminate or mucronate. Cymes dense. Fruiting perianth not inflated, green. Seeds smooth, mostly horizontal.{\i  S.E. Russia, S. Ukraine.} Rs(W, K, E).
\par

